msgid "Access Rights"
msgstr "Zugriffsrechte"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:5
msgid ""
"Activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, then go to "
":menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Groups`."
